### Get All Available Genres
GET http://localhost:3000/api/manga/genres

### Search for Colored Manga
POST http://localhost:3000/api/manga/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "filters": [
        {
            "field": "has_colored",
            "value": true,
            "action": "EQUALS",
            "score_multiplier": 1.2
        },
        {
            "field": "score",
            "value": 8.0,
            "action": "GREATER_THAN_OR_EQUALS",
            "score_multiplier": 1
        }
    ],
    "pagesize": 20
}

